Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我在網上查過了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 真島你也玩歌牌嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然不是那種經常在玩歌牌的閒人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不用多久 我就能超越你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天太一可是連足球練習也逃掉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 你真多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}あはでこのよを すくしてよとや
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}相逢無片刻 只嘆命將殘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 現在還不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好～!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀牌的時候 是一下也不能動的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}つゆにぬれつつ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滴滴冷露沾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}きみがため をしからざりし…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相思難從願 不惜下黃泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所知道的歌牌應該就像消磨時間的撲克牌一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌牌是一種運動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(750,80)\frz270\fn@方正大标宋_GBK\fad(300,200)}第三首
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(650,240)\fn@MHGHagoromoTHK-Medium\frz270\fad(300,300)}映明吉野天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在中盤送你的牌為什麼要放在這裡啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了 還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}老師 原田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等一會 正在反省中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 原田老師是這裡的負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他是個對歌牌無法放手的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個發出很大聲音的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是玩歌牌的孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 熱烈歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管別人說什麼 熱烈歡迎你們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}老師真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算每年兩次在本地區舉行啟蒙向的歌牌大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勸誘到的人不是一個就是兩個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而現在竟然一下子來三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 浩君你們這班傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴增加了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}註釋:ひろ和ひょろ讀音相似 其中ひょろ有搖晃和瘦弱的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晃君?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是浩! 木梨浩!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你們歌牌幾段了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我只記住了あ行和な行那一半而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 那是行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒記住就來這裡了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們安排的是比賽形式的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全無法相提並論呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種話比過再說吧 小晃君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是浩!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 我們就來場三對三的紅白戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿谷 比了也只是會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 太一 我們不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要比的話就要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂紅白戰即是團體戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把牌分成五十張 互相爭搶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你連這種事都不知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 小晃君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是放到真島你面前的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我所負責的牌嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是千早的 把它排成三行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有我還沒記得的牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排好的話 就開始15分鐘的背誦時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背誦時間?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是把排好的牌的位置記住的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果記不住這個的話 想贏就很難了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然自陣和敵陣都要記住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要記住一百個位置?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 我完全還沒記住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這15分鐘間去哪裡都行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到外面開個作戰會議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先千早負責的牌都是「一字決勝負」的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最開始讀到む或者す時馬上就能去取的牌總共有七張
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的都是些あ行的「二字決勝負」的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反過來 真島你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分配有叫做「大山札」的「六字決勝負」的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:04:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如「あさぼらけ」和「きみがため」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩張開頭五個字相同的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為需要猜牌 所以就叫「大山札」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}註釋：「大山」 詞源來自於「山を張る」意為：押寶、預測
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真島你也可以猜牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一讀到相應的牌就馬上去取
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要取的牌裡也有「五字決勝負」的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你叫我馬上去取…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是拿錯了牌怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都他說了算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}註釋:這幾個假名是指一字決勝負那些牌的頭一個字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「むすめふさほせ」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還搞什麼策略 綿谷你一個人跟小晃君他比不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有拖你後腿的人 不是能贏得更輕鬆嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想組成一個團體作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要組成一個團體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ほととぎす
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曙色朦朧裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才「一字決勝負」的牌應該是由我負責取的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你那麼慢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}きみがため はるののにいでて わかなつむ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}原上採春芽 只為獻君嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我負責的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了 猜錯牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我拿到那邊正確的牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為你拿錯牌了 所以對方要送過來一張牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等於各方各拿一張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大山札」的牌 我也會去取的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算真島你拿錯了 也能相抵消 所以放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼團體啊 這個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他完全沒想過要相信我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師那是發現寶物的感動姿勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個眼鏡君可不是一般的水平哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}むらさめの　つゆもまだひぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}驟雨頻頻降 枝頭露未乾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被搶先一步了 好不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一輪我不會輸給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼實力差距如此大卻還能不甘心的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:07:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西 明明沒必要那麼拼命的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算綿谷說要組成團隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也根本沒有期待我們做出什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}あさぼらけ うじのかわぎり たえだえに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}宇治臨拂曉 河灘冷霧中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我拿到正確的牌了 綿谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一張「あさぼらけ」開頭的牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜心聽 靜心聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜心聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ふくからに あきのくさきの しおるれば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枯焦憐草木 落葉逐飛蓬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 終於拿到一張了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}老師 對不起 痛不痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(394,440)}ふくからに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是「枯焦憐草木」開頭的牌嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒聽出「ふ」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 我可是出生到現在第一次像樣的取歌牌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是第一張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡那麼多有經驗的大人在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然只有這孩子動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我正式取到的第一張牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌牌真讓人爽快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前拿到牌的時候也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是我掉以輕心了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道取「一字決勝負」的牌 我輸給了千早?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些孩子真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來還是只拿到一張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只拿到五張 五張…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晃君 啊抱歉 浩君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的名字叫什麼? 要加入我們的歌牌會嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我加入 我叫綿谷新 小學六年級
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿谷新?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是從小學一年級到小學五年級
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在分年級組比賽裡 每年都全國優勝的那個傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:08:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起綿谷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他是八十年代七連霸的永世名人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福井綿谷始老師的孫子?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你們叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全記不住歌牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背得越多就越混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要背一百張絕對不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 但是你不是也有完全記住的牌嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(464,440)}ふくからに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天拿到的這張「枯焦憐草木」開頭的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(470,440)}ちはやふる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 就是「悠悠神代事」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿谷說那是我名字的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟自己深切相關的牌 就能比誰都要快拿到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百人一首總共有一百首
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當做能和一百個人交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地跟它們和睦相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睫毛君 你怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:10:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我要上補習班…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我會來的 盡可能地來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三月份有個大賽 你們在這裡努力練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大賽?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是三人一隊的團體戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是六年生能參加的最後的大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要參加 對吧 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要贏是吧 三個人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個大賽 是循環賽而不是紅白賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人當中就必須有兩個人贏才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然會贏 千早和太一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們其中一個給我要贏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特訓?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特訓…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特訓!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為早上有個廣告選秀 所以花了一筆買回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡這件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早真的是姐姐的第一號粉絲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還會說「我的夢想是姐姐成為日本第一的模特兒」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有自己想要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}こぬひとを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}思君終不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}やくやもしほの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}滷水釜中沸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得她對一件事情有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她一點優點都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只要不停地稱讚我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}やまがはに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濺濺山溪淌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作要更快更直接
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}やくやもしほの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滷水釜中沸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}よのなかは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬事應有定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あまのをぶねの つなでかなしも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠觀纖拉人 百感九迴腸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ありあけの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰看無情月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あかつきばかり うきものはなし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷腸唯此時 拂曉與君別
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}きみがため
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原上採春芽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 綿谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我新
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也要叫你新 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 新
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在一起玩歌牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}はなさ はなさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿院非 滿院非
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}はなさそ はなさそふ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿院非白 滿院非白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ふりゆくものは わがみなりけり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過眼雲煙散 身老嘆韶華
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真厲害 真島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考上開明成 真的很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說真島同學考上開明成中學了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他的第一志願不是秀西大附屬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能騎著自行車去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哪個笨蛋考上開明成還去秀西大附屬的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要花一個半鐘頭去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 你不會去那學校的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則就不能去老師那裡玩歌牌了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不能玩歌牌我也要去開明成 這不是明擺著的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 新
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一竟然說不能一起玩歌牌也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 在福井的爺爺病倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業之後我就要回福井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直在一起玩歌牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爺爺沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是腦溢血 還在住院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病的不輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去…不去比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 今天千早怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說是我的錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我要回福井
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不去歌牌大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她相處的時間比你長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下我一個人話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌牌一點樂趣都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個得還給老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 睫毛君不是很厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能考上開明成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是每個禮拜來歌牌會就能考上的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 流星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪 在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒看見嗎 真不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 眼鏡君的爺爺是歌牌的永世名人 很厲害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看就能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡君有他爺爺的教導才能那麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺病倒之後他該有多麼的擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又是流星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分 老師 真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你都不來的話 我會很寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是要跟你和好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是我出錢你寫字而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道千早會不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這麼小型的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 第一場對陣的胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是全國大賽的第二名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在跟他比大概贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來開始第一場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真島同學跟戴眼鏡的孩子一起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}千早振留隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 他們好像說今天要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早還沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是循環賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只要他們兩個贏了就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是決心今天一定要打敗綿谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你們的隊友是怕輸才不來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早只是遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓她不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了她會來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去買肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸給我之後就給你買肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為道口要等20分鐘才開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個只把我一個人丟下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是寂寞的不止是我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまをはるべと さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今兮春滿地 花開香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}たちわかれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下因幡道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}なにはがた みじかきあしの ふしのまも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短短蘆葦節 難波滿海灘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ちはやぶる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠悠神代事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牌在不斷減少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牌只有一百張
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不想結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不想結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不想結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 戴上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 真想把獎盃給千早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我能贏就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早也說句話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想 還想三個人一起玩歌牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 要拍咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開明成的西裝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 下一張跟我們拍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 媽媽去跟房東道別
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去把打包行李
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明天就搬家了 你自己的東西也要打包
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 你怎麼能一個人回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我玩歌牌吧 新
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真地決一勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忙著整理？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算對手只有5歲 我也不會手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}なにはづに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花開難波津
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一你讀的好死板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,0:19:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀牌要按照4-3-1-5的方式來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停頓方法是吧 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまをはるべと さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今兮春滿地 花開香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いにしへの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古都奈良城
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}わすらるる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誓遭遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}かぜをいたみ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風急波浪湧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了 贏的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有錄音帶 錄音帶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想是當上歌牌名人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟 我是因為與新相遇才愛上歌牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ちはやぶる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠悠神代事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時拿到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師說如果同時拿到由歌牌所在方為勝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的「千早」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起…玩歌牌 謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早和太一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:21:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 大概我們再也見不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有歌牌在 還會再見面的不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅持下去就還能再見面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能再見的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.34,0:01:25.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}帰り道は過ぎていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:28.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}少し風が吹いている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:34.11,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}たわいない会話妙に楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:39.01,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今でも変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:42.57,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕ら待ち合わせたあの場所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:48.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君はまだ覚えてるのかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:55.96,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今はちはやふる想い胸に抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:02:01.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目指した先に何があるんだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:07.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今なら掴めそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.89,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手を伸ばしてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:16.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢の途中きっといつかまた会えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.34,0:01:25.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}慢步走過回家的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:28.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}微風輕輕吹拂著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:34.11,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}閒話家常也異常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:39.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}至今依舊一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:42.57,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我們常常相約等候的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:48.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你可否仍然記得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:55.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在我心懷強烈的嚮往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:02:01.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}有什麼在目標之處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:07.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在的話似乎能抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.89,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}試著伸出雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:16.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在夢想的路上終有一天會再度重逢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:29.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}行くあてない街
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:34.82,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ひとり先を歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:40.07,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕日に照らされた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:45.14,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}失いそうな心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:50.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}変わってゆくなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:55.03,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想いもしなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:22:00.31,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君と重ねた夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:05.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつの間に違う方へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:09.11,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}歩いてたんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.29,0:22:14.47,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そしていま　ふたりは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:19.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遠すぎる世界見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:24.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そしていま　ほら　響くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:32.18,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君が教えてくれた歌　この空に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:29.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}向著無名的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:34.82,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}形單影隻地前進著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:40.07,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被夕陽照得通紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:45.14,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}近乎要遺失的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:50.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}卻逐漸發生了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:55.03,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我萬萬也沒有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:22:00.31,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}與你在一起的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:05.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不覺之間我們卻已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:09.11,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}走向了不同的道路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.29,0:22:14.47,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}於是此刻你我兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:19.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}凝望著遙不可及的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:24.90,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}於是此刻 你瞧 歌聲響徹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:32.18,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你曾經教會我唱的歌謠 迴響於這片天空
